<p><em><tt>The following documentation was recovered from a computer desk located in ██████, England. That lazy fuck probably just hasn't got out of bed yet. Also, the handwriting is really gross. Looks like an angry crow dipped its feet in ink and tried tap-dancing. Look, just- get on with it.</tt></em></p>
