<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/bittermixin-s-personnel-file/me.png" style="width:300px;" alt="me.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>Take a look at this goddamn poser.</p>
